    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duanzhengchun_6",
      "listener": "char_muwanqing_5",
      "text": "这‘五罗轻烟掌’，是我教你师父的。",
      "tone": "苦澀",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duanzhengchun_6",
      "listener": "char_muwanqing_5",
      "text": "婉儿，日后我要好好待你，方能补我一些过失。你有什么心愿，说给我听，我一定尽力给你办到。",
      "tone": "溫柔愧疚",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_muwanqing_5",
      "listener": "char_duanzhengchun_6",
      "text": "我和他的婚事，你要给我们作主，不许他负心薄幸。",
      "tone": "羞怯期待",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duanzhengchun_6",
      "listener": "char_muwanqing_5",
      "text": "你不能和誉儿成婚，也不能杀他。",
      "tone": "沉痛",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duanzhengchun_6",
      "listener": "char_muwanqing_5",
      "text": "因为……因为……因为段誉是你的亲哥哥！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_muwanqing_5",
      "listener": "char_duanzhengchun_6",
      "text": "我不信！我不信！我……我不信！",
